{"tid":981392,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Texas 炸雞","createTime":"2019-01-14T09:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T06:49:28.000Z","uid":175988,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a9f0ed9ba0f2ec8005b95fb8b0588de6b39147af","tid":981392,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:20:51.000Z","msg":"<strong>Raising Cane's Chicken Fingers @ Texas</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DZbLPpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDZbLPpt.jpg&h=8851657d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>Box Combo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炸雞皮脆肉滑，炸皮調味適中，夠薄又唔會太硬，雞肉鬆軟多汁，食落好c服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTexas Toast (似厚切排包) 烘至金黃，包身軟綿，面頭少少脆，加上牛油簡直無得輸<br />\n自由斟嘅冰茶嘅茶底唔錯，少甜，有茶葉香味又唔澀，清爽解膩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醬汁係有少少胡椒味嘅沙律醬，同雞肉幾夾但唔太特別<br />\n薯條夠脆但係薯蓉唔夠軟糯，外皮偏硬<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論：好食過依家香港任何一間連鎖快餐嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，Texas fried chicken 果然唔係浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"500af3b8f589754afdc15bf40b6a4768d6283156","tid":981392,"uid":175988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003844491dc6c7ffee3b8cb87f7ac3bee8b4d3c1","tid":981392,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"幾錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d7128d4cd97f8094925547e7bc7b42301e89e5b","tid":981392,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"003844491dc6c7ffee3b8cb87f7ac3bee8b4d3c1","tid":981392,"uid":138197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit